          "text": "<2000g\n40mg/kg/day IM/IV divided q12h\nFirst Dose: 20mg/kg IM/IV x 1\nMax 6g/day\n>2000g\n60mg/kg/day IM/IV divided q8h\nFirst Dose: 20mg/kg IM/IV x 1\nMax 6g/day",
          "tables": []
        },
        "General_(>1_Month)": {
          "text": "25-100mg/kg/day IM/IV divided q6-8h\nFirst Dose: 20-33mg/kg IM/IV x 1\nMax 6g/day",
